        <div class="ip-model-card">
          <div class="ip-model-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ip-model-title">iPhone 14 &amp; 13 Series</h3>
          <p class="ip-model-description">Pro camera systems and A15/A16 chips. Affordable same-day screen and battery repairs for all variants.</p>
          <div class="ip-model-pills">
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 14 Pro Max</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 14 Pro</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 14 Plus</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 14</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 13 Pro Max</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 13 Pro</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 13 mini</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 13</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://shop.mobiletechlab.ca/pages/repair2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ip-model-cta">
            Get Quote &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="ip-model-card">
          <div class="ip-model-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ip-model-title">iPhone 12, 11 &amp; X Series</h3>
          <p class="ip-model-description">Face ID models with OLED displays. Affordable screen and battery replacement for all Face ID iPhones.</p>
          <div class="ip-model-pills">
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 12 Pro Max</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 12 Pro</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 12 mini</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 12</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 11 Pro Max</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 11 Pro</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 11</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone XS Max</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone XS</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone XR</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone X</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://shop.mobiletechlab.ca/pages/repair2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ip-model-cta">
            Get Quote &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="ip-model-card">
          <div class="ip-model-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ip-model-title">iPhone SE &amp; Legacy</h3>
          <p class="ip-model-description">Older iPhones and SE models still repaired. Parts available for most legacy models — contact us to confirm availability for your specific model.</p>
          <div class="ip-model-pills">
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone SE (3rd Gen)</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone SE (2nd Gen)</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone SE (1st Gen)</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 8 Plus</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 8</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 7 Plus</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 7</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 6s Plus</span>
            <span class="ip-pill">iPhone 6s</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://shop.mobiletechlab.ca/pages/repair2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ip-model-cta">
            Get Quote &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="ip-why-section" id="why-choose-us">
    <div class="ip-container">
      <div class="ip-section-header">
        <h2 class="ip-section-title">The Mobile Tech Lab Advantage: Winnipeg's iPhone Repair Experts</h2>
        <p class="ip-section-subtitle">Why thousands of Winnipeg customers trust us with their iPhones</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ip-pillars-grid">
        <div class="ip-pillar-card">
          <div class="ip-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ip-pillar-title">Apple IRP Certified</h3>
          <p class="ip-pillar-body">Mobile Tech Lab is an Apple Independent Repair Provider — giving us access to genuine Apple parts, official diagnostics, and specialized tools. This means your iPhone repair meets Apple's own quality standards without the Apple Store price tag.</p>
        </div>
