      <div class="ip-faq-list">
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>How long does iPhone screen replacement take in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Most iPhone screen replacements at our Winnipeg shop are completed in 1–2 hours while you wait. We stock screens for all popular iPhone models so walk-in same-day service is available at our St. Vital location.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Do you offer same-day iPhone battery replacement in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Yes — same-day iPhone battery replacement is available for all models at our Winnipeg St. Vital location. Most battery swaps take under an hour and your phone is returned fully tested before you leave.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Are your iPhone repair parts genuine Apple or aftermarket?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">We use high-quality parts that meet or exceed OEM standards for most repairs, and genuine Apple parts are available for customers who prefer them. As an Apple Independent Repair Provider, we have access to official Apple parts and diagnostics.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Do I need an appointment for iPhone repair in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">No appointment is needed — walk-ins are welcome at both our St. Vital and Thompson locations any time during business hours. Booking ahead helps us confirm we have your specific model's parts ready, which can speed up your repair.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>What warranty do you offer on iPhone repairs?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Screen repairs carry a 30-day to lifetime warranty depending on the part tier selected. Battery replacements include a 90-day warranty, and most other component repairs carry a lifetime warranty on parts and labour.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>What if I find a cheaper iPhone repair quote in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">We offer a price match guarantee — show us a lower quote from any Winnipeg repair shop for the same repair and we'll match it. We believe you shouldn't have to pay more than necessary for a quality iPhone fix.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Can you repair an iPhone that won't turn on?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Yes — a completely unresponsive iPhone is often caused by a fully drained battery, a failed display connection, or a software issue. We run free diagnostics before recommending any repair so you know exactly what the issue is.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Do you repair iPhone back glass in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Yes — we replace cracked back glass on iPhone 8 and all newer models including the full iPhone 16 lineup. Back glass repair requires full disassembly of the device, so it takes a bit longer than a screen replacement.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Can you fix iPhone water damage in Winnipeg?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Yes — despite water resistance ratings, iPhones can still suffer liquid damage from salt water, pool chemicals, or older models with degraded seals. We perform ultrasonic cleaning and component-level diagnostics to assess what can be recovered.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ip-faq-item">
          <summary class="ip-faq-summary">
            <span>Do you repair iPhones in Thompson, MB?</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ip-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="ip-faq-answer">Yes — our Thompson location at 300 Mystery Lake Rd #1530 offers the same iPhone repair services as Winnipeg. Walk-ins are welcome Monday through Saturday 10AM–6PM.</p>
